title: Fund Administration Management System
description: Collaborated with a team of developers to build a robust fund administration system, encompassing:
details: Member Management: Streamlined onboarding and data management for individual members.
Company Management: Oversaw company enrollment and tracking within the system.
Fund Management: Enabled creation and maintenance of diverse fund structures.
Contributions: Automated the processing and allocation of contributions.
Claims: Focused on optimizing claim submissions and processing workflows.
Dynamic Reports: Designed flexible reporting tools for real-time insights.

title: Data Migration & Cleanup
description: Led data migration project, transferring data between SQL Server and PostgreSQL, ensuring data integrity and minimizing downtime.
details: Designed and implemented ETL (Extract, Transform, Load) processes for efficient data migration and integration.
Utilized tools like SSMS (SQL Server Management Studio) and custom scripts to automate data migration tasks.
Conducted data validation and testing post-migration to ensure accuracy and consistency.
